data.description: Don't miss out on this opportunity to experience small town living with easy access to I-49 for NW Arkansas conveniences!Classic full brick home in Pineville. Freshly remodeled with new interior finishes, includes new doors, paint, and premium laminate floors. Everything is clean, beautiful and move-in ready! Has split floor plan and a 13x20 bonus room, which makes great media or game rm or home office!Includes 2 nice outbuildings with 300 sq ft of storage, including an overhead door. All this on a lovely, rolling, shaded .70 acre lot Located on a quiet cul-de-sac in a quiet subdivision with only a short walk to historic downtown Pineville, and the Elk River. Close access to Big and Little Sugar Creeks and Indian Creek! Sale includes lots 11, and 14, of Halls Hill Estates.
